    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Young women think that it is menial to cook and do other kinds of housework; and, for this reason, many girls who marry and have the care of families have little idea of the duties devolving upon a wife and mother.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">3<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"MH 302.1\" data-link=\"135.1531\">The Ministry of Healing, 302</span>.</span></a></sup>",
